{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-44","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada neko koristi pitanje kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">did you?</span> na kraju rečenice, obično traži potvrdu o tome što veruje da je istina. Ovo je način provere informacija. Obično se sastoji korišćenjem pomoćnog glagola (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to be</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have</span>, ili modalnog glagola) zajedno sa subjektom.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ako je glavna rečenica pozitivna, oznaka postaje negativna. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">You studied programming, didn't you?</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako je glavna rečenica negativna, oznaka postaje pozitivna. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">You didn't study programming, did you?</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Tokom razgovora, Brian dodaje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">did you?</span> nakon svoje izjave kako bi proverio da li je tačno ono što misli o iskustvu Sofije u programu.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-44"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta Brian pokušava da sazna od Sophie?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Ako uživa u programu.</p>","feedback":"<p>Pitanje Braiana nije bilo posebno o tome da li uživa u programu.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako je imao mnogo kućnih poslova.</p>","feedback":"<p>Brian pita posebno o projektima softvera.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako je radio/radila na mnogim softverskim projektima.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako je nedavno studirao program.</p>","feedback":"<p>Pitanje Briana se fokusira na njegovo iskustvo tokom studija, a ne nužno na to kada je učio.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Brian","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"3.1-3.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":17.98,"finishTimestamp":23.26},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":6.28,"dialogue":{"text":"That's interesting. So you didn't work on many programming projects during your studies, did you?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":6.78,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 44","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background","dashedName":"task-44","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-45","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-43","id":"65f3234e85f828dd1f45d384","s